{
  "name": "Prayer of Healing",
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You incite a prayer that upon completion you have a pool of healing equal to [[/r 12d6]] + your spellcasting ability modifier which you roll and add up. This pool of healing is then immediately used on up to six creatures of your choice within range to regain hit points. Any unused healing from the pool is lost. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels</strong>. When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the healing increases by [[/r 2d6]] for each slot level above 2nd.</p>",
